## Table Descriptions

### Workflow Domain

| Table                 | Description                                                                  |
| --------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Workflow**          | Main workflow definitions with JSON markup containing workflow configuration |
| **WorkflowLink**      | Links workflows to spaces or content items, enabling/disabling them          |
| **WorkflowLabel**     | Labels associated with workflows for filtering/categorization                |
| **WorkflowVersion**   | Version history tracking changes to workflow markup                          |
| **WorkflowParameter** | Workflow-scoped parameter values applied at space level                      |

### Content State Domain

| Table                       | Description                                                                    |
| --------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ |
| **ContentState**            | Current state of content within a workflow (state name, approval status, etc.) |
| **ContentStateLabel**       | Labels associated with content for workflow matching                           |
| **ContentApproval**         | Approval requirements for content at a given state                             |
| **ContentApprovalDecision** | Individual user decisions (approve/reject) for approvals                       |

### Content Parameters Domain

| Table                           | Description                                     |
| ------------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------- |
| **ContentParameterAndMetadata** | Page-scoped parameters and their current values |
| **ContentParameterHistory**     | Historical versions of content parameters       |

### Messaging Domain

| Table        | Description                                                         |
| ------------ | ------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Messages** | System messages (info/warning/error) displayed to users for content |

### Document Activity Domain

| Table                     | Description                                                    |
| ------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **DocumentActivity**      | Activity log tracking all workflow-related events for content  |
| **DocumentActivityUsers** | Users involved in specific activities (for multi-user actions) |

