## Foreign Key Constraints

The schema has **only one explicit foreign key constraint**:

| Table                 | Column     | References           | On Delete |
| --------------------- | ---------- | -------------------- | --------- |
| DocumentActivityUsers | activityId | DocumentActivity(id) | CASCADE   |

All other relationships are **logical/implicit** based on column naming conventions (e.g., `contentId`, `workflowId`) but are **not enforced by FK constraints** at the database level.

